36:17.280 --> 36:20.530
The Achillea Bead Tournament will span three days.

36:21.070 --> 36:24.460
May all disciples from every peak give their full effort.

36:25.070 --> 36:28.460
Prepare yourselves for the coming Sea Calamity.

36:38.440 --> 36:41.130
All disciples from the sixteen peaks must participate.

36:41.710 --> 36:42.610
By the end of the Wu hour,

36:43.230 --> 36:45.860
sixteen winners will advance to the second round.

36:46.630 --> 36:49.050
From the Wei hour onward, the top eight will be decided.

36:49.920 --> 36:52.490
To ensure each peak has a disciple in the second round,

36:53.710 --> 36:55.860
Zhuiyu Peak gets a bye in the first round.

36:58.230 --> 36:59.570
- Really? - That's great!

37:06.400 --> 37:09.420
Cuixuan, isn't that unfair?

37:10.150 --> 37:12.820
Baifu, have you lost your mind?

37:14.000 --> 37:16.010
Under Cuixuan's leadership, Wuyue Court

37:16.440 --> 37:17.530
has never been unfair.

37:18.070 --> 37:19.260
How could it be unfair?

37:19.710 --> 37:21.300
We're about to start. Stop your nonsense.

37:21.920 --> 37:22.740
Shut your mouth.

37:26.510 --> 37:28.340
Let the tournament begin!

38:00.510 --> 38:01.460
Amazing.

38:24.070 --> 38:25.010
As expected of Qin.

38:25.590 --> 38:26.090
Incredible.

38:51.800 --> 38:52.740
Lifei, hurry.

38:53.030 --> 38:54.530
Lei has already won six matches.

38:54.550 --> 38:55.340
Everyone says it's spectacular.

38:55.510 --> 38:57.300
If we're late, we'll miss the best parts.

38:58.480 --> 38:59.260
Lei is really impressive.

38:59.280 --> 39:00.690
- As expected of Lei. - Yeah.

39:00.710 --> 39:01.610
Absolutely amazing.

39:02.190 --> 39:03.650
Lei is incredible!

39:04.590 --> 39:05.940
Were you two really fellow disciples?

39:07.800 --> 39:08.610
What are you implying?

39:09.320 --> 39:11.690
Nothing. Just that

39:12.110 --> 39:16.460
talent levels differ, and quality varies.

39:17.880 --> 39:18.340
You...

39:18.360 --> 39:18.860
Lifei.

39:19.550 --> 39:21.260
The name tag for your second-round opponent is out.

39:21.760 --> 39:22.420
Who am I facing?

39:22.630 --> 39:23.260
Deng Xiguang.

39:23.550 --> 39:24.380
Deng?

39:24.630 --> 39:26.380
That's Elder Baifu's top disciple.

39:26.400 --> 39:27.050
Deng Xiguang?

39:29.510 --> 39:30.460
It's okay, Lifei.

39:31.030 --> 39:32.130
Just going through the motions.

39:34.480 --> 39:38.900
Remember my name! I'm Deng Xiguang!

39:41.670 --> 39:42.530
I have an idea.

39:47.760 --> 39:48.740
As the Sage taught,

39:48.920 --> 39:50.530
extend the respect and care

39:50.920 --> 39:52.610
you show your own family to others as well.

39:53.070 --> 39:54.300
As your senior,

39:54.960 --> 39:55.860
I'll go easy on you

39:56.440 --> 39:58.490
and let you lose with dignity.

40:04.880 --> 40:06.570
Deng, you're such a good person.

40:06.960 --> 40:07.780
Please accept my bow.

40:38.030 --> 40:38.380
Lime powder?

40:38.400 --> 40:39.210
Sorry, Deng.

40:39.440 --> 40:40.460
I'm too busy training

40:40.480 --> 40:41.420
to wash my clothes.

40:41.440 --> 40:42.210
It's all dust. See?

40:42.400 --> 40:43.530
See?

40:49.280 --> 40:50.460
As the Sage taught,

40:51.360 --> 40:54.420
winning unfairly is dishonorable, but yielding shows...

40:55.550 --> 40:56.900
virtue!

40:58.150 --> 40:59.050
Did he faint from shock?

40:59.070 --> 41:00.340
- How did he faint? - He just fainted?

41:04.760 --> 41:05.460
No way.

41:05.840 --> 41:06.740
That's one way to do it.

41:06.760 --> 41:07.820
Didn't see that coming.

41:10.590 --> 41:11.210
I won!

41:12.440 --> 41:13.170
Which peak is she from?

41:13.190 --> 41:14.090
Which peak is she from?

41:15.230 --> 41:15.570
Yeah.

41:15.590 --> 41:16.780
Is she from Zhuiyu Peak?

41:17.480 --> 41:19.420
I don't know. I don't recognize her.

41:19.920 --> 41:20.820
I don't know her!

41:23.670 --> 41:24.690
Outrageous!

41:25.320 --> 41:28.650
Can such a despicable win even count?

41:28.670 --> 41:30.460
Baifu, watch your words.

41:30.710 --> 41:31.780
What do you mean, despicable?

41:32.230 --> 41:34.050
That's called strategy and quick thinking.

41:34.630 --> 41:37.090
Magic is a contest of both power and strategy.

41:37.590 --> 41:38.130
Don't you understand?

41:39.880 --> 41:41.740
She truly has her master's style.

41:41.840 --> 41:43.780
Yes. She's my disciple. What of it?

41:44.320 --> 41:45.210
As expected of your disciple.

41:51.400 --> 41:55.530
The top eight are set. Tomorrow will determine the top four.

41:56.230 --> 41:57.820
Jiang Lifei versus Tang De.

41:58.440 --> 42:00.170
Qin Yangling versus Cheng Feng.

42:01.070 --> 42:02.650
Yue Cailing versus Ban Tou.

42:03.480 --> 42:05.780
Lei Xiuyuan versus Wu Jiahui.

42:20.800 --> 42:22.340
All participating disciples

42:22.510 --> 42:24.490
have taken enough demon-purging water.

42:25.190 --> 42:27.340
Any who have secretly practiced demonic arts

42:28.070 --> 42:31.050
will lose control and be exposed tonight.

42:42.050 --> 42:43.000
